==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From {{proto|Indo-European|ḱwṓ|lang=grc}}. Cognates include Latin {{term|canis|lang=la}}, Sanskrit {{term|sc=Deva|श्वन्|tr=śván|lang=sa}} and Old English {{term|hund|lang=ang}} (English {{term|hound}}).

